title: MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 23
text:
MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 23 
By DONOVAN KLEIN - 21ALIVE October 24, 2015 Updated Oct 24, 2015 at 12:23 AM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, IND. (21ALIVE) - 21Alive's Tommy Schoegler and AWP President and CEO Michael Ledo break down the big high school football games of the night. 
Sectionals began this week which means the promise of more game to play for many schools and the ending of many seasons as well. The guys look forward to next week's match-ups to see who will move one step closer to the state title.
